# Recordings policy (v6 plan task 3.4):
#   * .mov / .mp4 masters → gitignore (200 MB+ each typical; 3.6 produces
#     fresh ones, prior takes stay on disk locally as rehearsal context
#     but don't ship in the repo).
#   * recordings/final.mp4 — the FINAL exported video tracked separately
#     ONLY if size stays under a sensible cap (judgment call in 3.6;
#     YouTube unlisted URL is the canonical pointer either way).
#   * recordings/voiceover/*.m4a stems — tracked, ≤3 MB total, useful
#     submission-grade evidence + remix material if a single segment
#     needs a re-mix without re-recording all seven.
recordings/*.mov
recordings/*.mp4
!recordings/final.mp4
